** __ Java String__ **
=> Strings are used to store text.
=> String variables contains a collections of characters surrounded by double quotes. (" ")
eg. String name = "Java"

String methods
    .length()
    .charAt(index)
    .indexof("");
    .lastIndexof("")
    .toUpperCase()
    .toLowerCase()
    .trim()
    .replace("","");
    .isEmpty() /boolean
    .contains()
    .equals();
    .equalsIgnoreCase();

    .subString(start, end) // substring method used to extract a portion of a string.